title: Israel Monthly Wages in Manufacturing Index
description: Wages in Manufacturing in Israel decreased to 126.10 points in August from 126.50 points in July of 2022. Wages in Manufacturing in Israel averaged 113.93 points from 2005 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 149.40 points in March of 2021 and a record low of 96 points in November of 2013. This page provides - Israel Monthly Wages in Manufacturing Index - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bureau of Statistics, Israel
